cat("There are approximately 7,400,000,000 people on Earth. These people are split into 7 continents and 196 countries. There are roughly 6,500 languages that are spoken today. The Earth has been around for about 4.5 billion years, with one year being a full orbit around the Sun. Much of society today is centered on popular culture, social media, and technology. Popular social media websites and applications include Facebook, Instagram, Snapchat, and Twitter.")